.
 This relation is denoted as 
\begin_inset Formula $\nu<<\mu$
\end_inset

 symbolically.
 We discuss absolute continuity in Chapter 6, where we prove the converse
 of this theorem under a minor restriction.
 The non-negative measurable function 
\begin_inset Formula $f$
\end_inset

 which generates the new measure 
